OOC: Yes, Carnage, when i say Raptor, i mean Velociraptor, not Utahraptor or 
Oviraptor, or any others.

:::Wheeljack:::

Wheeljack: Well, so far ive extended the shields of this mighty warship to 
reach across the entire island.  It was very useful in a recent battle.  
Besides those things, not much.  As Zardus said, we should be able to make a 
powerful defence system with our combined knowledge.  My goal is to make this 
base more powerful then the Cybertronian Fire, the Maximal Base.  Alright.  
Lets get to work. I'll design the systems, and you help me out with how to 
use them and where to place them.
::He starts working::

--part1_f3.75257be.27b46f50_boundary
